{"tid":862222,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"無啊..我無喊..","createTime":"2018-10-14T16:39:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T07:46:27.000Z","uid":208125,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"13ed4fa08aa9d540f5a46494b8ed3f05991fe42f","tid":862222,"uid":208125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T16:39:30.000Z","msg":"我份人本身比較開朗<br />\n好中意做朋友嘅小丑氹佢地笑<br />\n就算唔開心都唔想比佢地知<br />\n所以就算岩岩比人鬧完<br />\n喊都唔太想喊出聲<br />\n只會忍住望住自己嘅眼淚一滴一滴咁滴落黎<br />\n喊完朋友見到我眼紅紅地問我做咩喊 <br />\n我只可以笑笑口講我無喊<br />\n呢種感覺真係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再咁落去真係覺得自己會抑鬱<br />\nfml<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86dbe8c8f975976957b470137ca30a2e51ea69ca","tid":862222,"uid":208542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T16:43:45.000Z","msg":"俾人鬧啲咩搞到想喊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361e90519f004d2f2d2d0223f84e551d4d161d5c","tid":862222,"uid":208125,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"86dbe8c8f975976957b470137ca30a2e51ea69ca","tid":862222,"uid":208542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T16:43:45.000Z","msg":"俾人鬧啲咩搞到想喊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T16:44:44.000Z","msg":"總之成日小小野比人鬧 好辛苦 you know that bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d67fe952f28183c01e17efd0ec34c066af55338b","tid":862222,"uid":123456,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T16:45:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">f你老母ml咩<br />\n抵啦死賤種</span>"},{"pid":"b1a93a3c46c2370db5988ee8550a0efb92d2e398","tid":862222,"uid":208125,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d67fe952f28183c01e17efd0ec34c066af55338b","tid":862222,"uid":123456,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T16:45:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">f你老